# Dashboard navigation

Sidebar labels and paths are defined only in `components/dashboard/sidebar.tsx`:

- Use the exported `navigation` array — do **not** create separate nav config files (e.g. `lib/config/dashboard-navigation.ts`).
- AI prompts: use `buildDashboardNavPromptSection()` from the same file (consumed by `lib/ai-assistant/snapshot.ts`).
- **Calendar** in the sidebar maps to `/dashboard/schedule` (not `/dashboard/calendar`).
- **Auto Follow-Up** → `/dashboard/leads/sequences` (UI may show **AI Auto Follow-Up** when the AI auto-lead addon is active).
- Marketing sub-tabs live in `components/marketing/marketing-tabs.tsx`; prompt text is mirrored in `sidebar.tsx` (`MARKETING_SUB_NAV_FOR_PROMPT`) — keep both in sync when changing marketing routes.
